WEBVTT

18:34.680 --> 18:36.350 line:80%
But of all virtues,
filial piety comes first.

18:36.350 --> 18:38.390 line:80%
If I defied my mother
and insisted on marrying you,

18:38.390 --> 18:40.850 line:80%
I'd become an unfilial
and unrighteous man.

18:41.910 --> 18:43.350 line:80%
Although we cannot
become husband and wife,

18:43.350 --> 18:44.960 line:80%
we can be like brother and sister.
